-- Brazil to Prioritize Sustainable Products in Purchases: Rousseff
-- B y   K a t e r i n a   P e t r o f f
-- 2012-06-11T10:11:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-11/brazil-to-prioritize-sustainable-products-in-purchases-rousseff.html
Brazil will prioritize sustainable
products in government purchases, President  Dilma Rousseff  said
today in her weekly radio program.  “We will continue to pursue a development based on growth,
inclusion and protection,” Rousseff said. “This is what we’ll
present at the Rio+20 Conference later this week.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katerina Petroff in Sao Paulo at 
 kpetroff@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Leonardo Lara at 
